title: Over-the-door hook rack

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for an over-the-door hook rack, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a perspective view of an over-the-door hook rack, showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is a front elevational view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a top plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 5 is a perspective view of a second embodiment of an over-the-door hook rack.

The jagged lines shown in the drawing disclosure are meant to represent indeterminate length. The broken lines shown in the drawing disclosure are for illustrative purposes only and form no part of the claimed design.
